604
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,000
Be careful.

605
00:31:29,450 --> 00:31:32,880
[Qingli, a butterfly demon]

606
00:31:44,310 --> 00:31:45,200
Qingli.

607
00:31:45,550 --> 00:31:46,400
Qingli!

608
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:47,400
