619
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:22,000
See you.

620
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:30,480
Qingli.

621
00:32:37,350 --> 00:32:39,480
You've been gone for half a month.

622
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:43,310
This time,

623
